'''''Mythprint''''' '''(Vol.11, No.1)''' is an issue of the bulletin ''[[Mythprint]]''.

The issue reprints "J.R.R. Tolkien - The Wizard Father" by Michael Tolkien from ''The Sunday Telegraph''.
